><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 17, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104guy1665703174644.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/guy1665703174644.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/guy1665703174644.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"guy1665703174644\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Encode the contents of <code class=\"ph codeph\">InBuf</code> and place the result in <code class=\"ph codeph\">OutBuf</code>.\n </p> <section class=\"section\" id=\"guy1665703174644__section_w3676ab1b5b1_w3677ab1b5_w3678ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d872944e55\">Return Values</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"guy1665703174644__parml_vss_wd1_fwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\">USEC_SUCCESS</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Encode successful, no info returned </dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\">USEC_ERROR</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Encode failed, error returned in Error members </dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"guy1665703174644__section_w3679ab1b5b3_w3680ab1b5_w3681ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d872944e82\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"guy1665703174644__p_d132200e1_d132201e1_d132202e1\">Encode the data in <code class=\"ph codeph\">InBuf</code> of length\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">InDataLen</code>. The encoded data must be placed in <code class=\"ph codeph\">OutBuf</code> and\n        its length in <code class=\"ph codeph\">OutDataLen</code>, which must be less than or equal to\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">OutBufLen</code>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"guy1665703174644__p_d132203e1_d132204e1_d132205e1\">If the output buffer is not large enough to hold the\n        encoded data, return an error.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"guy1665703174644__section_r55_121_fwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d872944e109\">SMTP</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"guy1665703174644__p_d132209e1_d132210e1_d132211e1\">For an SMTP driver, this function is called after\n        successful initialization. It is given the message that is to be sent to the SMTP server and\n        it returns a message that is signed, encrypted, or reformatted .</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528045\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528045\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "USEC_ENCODE Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 17, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Encode the contents of InBuf and place the result in OutBuf . Return Values USEC_SUCCESS Encode successful, no info returned USEC_ERROR Encode failed, error returned in Error members Description Encode the data in InBuf of length InDataLen . The encoded data must be placed in OutBuf and its length in OutDataLen , which must be less than or equal to OutBufLen . If the output buffer is not large enough to hold the encoded data, return an error. SMTP For an SMTP driver, this function is called after successful initialization. It is given the message that is to be sent to the SMTP server and it returns a message that is signed, encrypted, or reformatted . Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}